# wf workspace — personal shared-context repo.
# The workspace root holds four independent git repos (match, hamster,
# orchestrator, commons-kotlin) plus scratch and build artifacts. Track only
# the shared context: this file, the workspace CLAUDE.md, and whContext/.

# Ignore everything at the workspace root by default...
/*

# ...then re-include only the shared-context pieces.
!/.gitignore
!/CLAUDE.md
!/whContext/
